text: Jessica Tomasi is an Italian archer. She was born on 3 July 1986. Tomasi competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics.Jessica TomasiJessica TOMASI ==Biography== Jessica Tomasi started archery in 1996. She entered her first international competitions in 2000. Her first global podium came in 2011 when she won the gold in the women's classic archery team event. == References == Category:Italian archers Category:Olympians for Italy Category:1986 births Category:Living people
